    They can take care of him.

1316
00:57:25,245 --> 00:57:26,413
Come on,
let's get out of here.

1317
00:57:26,479 --> 00:57:29,082
Dennis, listen to me.

1318
00:57:29,149 --> 00:57:30,417
Something's going on here.

1319
00:57:30,483 --> 00:57:32,752
