Yeah, I'm gonna be all right.

1324
00:57:41,828 --> 00:57:43,163
All right.

1325
00:57:44,764 --> 00:57:46,366
All right,
merry Christmas, partner, huh?

1326
00:57:46,433 --> 00:57:47,567
Merry Christmas.

1327
00:57:47,634 --> 00:57:48,568
Whoa.

1328
00:57:48,635 --> 00:57:49,536
I didn't see
nothing.

1329
00:57:49,602 --> 00:57:50,537
What is it
with this guy?

1330
00:57:50,603 --> 00:57:51,638
You don't even
want to know.

1331
00:57:51,705 --> 00:57:53,139
All right, later.

1332
00:57:53,206 --> 00:57:55,475
Take care.

1333
00:57:59,412 --> 00:58:01,614
[sighs]

