00:58:01,748 --> 00:58:03,116
This is really hot.

1335
00:58:03,183 --> 00:58:04,384
Be careful.

1336
00:58:04,451 --> 00:58:05,585
It's tea
  with bitters.

1337
00:58:05,652 --> 00:58:07,320
It's good
      for your stomach.

1338
00:58:07,387 --> 00:58:08,588
Thanks for letting me
come here.

1339
00:58:08,655 --> 00:58:09,589
Oh, sure.

1340
00:58:09,656 --> 00:58:10,557
It's not right,
you know.

1341
00:58:10,623 --> 00:58:12,092
I should be the one
helping you.

1342
00:58:12,158 --> 00:58:13,693
Oh, no, I'm the one
  that always

1343
00:58:13,760 --> 00:58:15,762
takes care of everybody,
      remember?

1344
00:58:15,829 --> 00:58:17,097
My thing.

1345
00:58:17,163 --> 00:58:18,798
Must be something
      you need, though.

1346
00:58:18,865 --> 00:58:19,866
What do you mean?

1347
00:58:19,933 --> 00:58:21,267
Well,

1348
00:58:21,334 --> 00:58:23,169
what do you want most
      in the whole world, Rose?

1349
00:58:27,674 --> 00:58:31,444
I guess just to make it
through the night would be nice.

1350
00:58:31,511 --> 00:58:33,747
