1379
00:59:39,412 --> 00:59:41,081
You have to speak
    to another doctor.

1380
00:59:41,147 --> 00:59:42,248
For what?

1381
00:59:42,315 --> 00:59:43,616
Those are the rules.

1382
00:59:43,683 --> 00:59:46,019
Look, you can't
    just keep me here.

1383
00:59:46,086 --> 00:59:47,721
I can't,
but he can.

1384
00:59:50,457 --> 00:59:51,858
Now sit down.

1385
00:59:55,428 --> 00:59:56,930
[both chuckle]

1386
00:59:59,032 --> 01:00:02,836
Charlie, I hope
you don't mind my asking, but...

1387
01:00:02,902 --> 01:00:06,272
Why did you leave the priesthood
after 20 years?

1388
01:00:09,109 --> 01:00:10,710
I lost my faith.

1389
01:00:13,146 --> 01:00:16,416
And I began to question
      the existence of God.

1390
01:00:16,483 --> 01:00:19,753
If you're a priest,
that's not good.

1391
01:00:19,819 --> 01:00:22,655
So here I am.

1392
01:00:22,722 --> 01:00:23,623
I'm sorry.

1393
01:00:23,690 --> 01:00:24,891
It's all right.

1394
01:00:26,459 --> 01:00:28,094
What about you?
What about me?

1395
01:00:28,161 --> 01:00:29,229
How's your faith?

1396
01:00:29,295 --> 01:00:30,330
Oh, it's pretty shaky.

1397
01:00:30,397 --> 01:00:31,531
Really?
  Why?

1398
01:00:32,999 --> 01:00:34,434
Well, my mom's been sick

1399
01:00:34,501 --> 01:00:36,069
for a long time
      with Alzheimer's,

1400
01:00:36,136 --> 01:00:37,470
and she was always the glue

1401
01:00:37,537 --> 01:00:38,972
that kind of
      kept the family together.

1402
01:00:39,039 --> 01:00:40,807
Now she can't even
bathe herself.

1403
01:00:40,874 --> 01:00:43,576
And I keep trying
to reconnect with her.

1404
01:00:43,643 --> 01:00:45,412
How do you do that
  with someone who's not there?

1405
01:00:45,478 --> 01:00:48,281
Well, I put...

1406
01:00:48,348 --> 01:00:50,150
I put pictures of the family
  all around the room,

1407
01:00:50,216 --> 01:00:51,518
and I bring her
    her favorite foods.

1408
01:00:51,584 --> 01:00:52,819
I play her favorite music.

1409
01:00:52,886 --> 01:00:54,154
You know,
    I'm just trying to find her

1410
01:00:54,220 --> 01:00:56,456
just even for, like,
      a second,

1411
01:00:56,523 --> 01:00:59,059
just to have some kind
of moment of clarity, you know,

1412
01:00:59,125 --> 01:01:02,028
so that I know
    she's still there.

1413
01:01:02,095 --> 01:01:05,065
Does it work?

1414
01:01:05,131 --> 01:01:08,735
No.

1415
01:01:08,802 --> 01:01:10,704
Do you pray?

1416
01:01:10,770 --> 01:01:13,406
No, not anymore.

1417
01:01:13,473 --> 01:01:15,575
Yeah, I know
  how that is.

1418
01:01:21,648 --> 01:01:23,650
Only five more hours
to go.

1419
01:01:23,717 --> 01:01:25,852
Till what?

1420
01:01:25,919 --> 01:01:27,987
Till you make it
    through the night.

1421
01:01:32,992 --> 01:01:35,195
This is mesmerizing.

1422
01:01:35,261 --> 01:01:36,296
Not for five hours.

1423
01:01:36,363 --> 01:01:37,397
No.

1424
01:01:37,464 --> 01:01:38,932
We should put
      another tape on.

1425
01:01:43,370 --> 01:01:44,704
How you doing?

1426
