Look, I want
to go home now!

1428
01:01:48,808 --> 01:01:50,310
All right?
    This is all wrong.

1429
01:01:50,377 --> 01:01:52,579
This is not the way
  it's supposed to be!

1430
01:01:52,645 --> 01:01:53,747
Calm down, Mr. Calvert.

1431
01:01:53,813 --> 01:01:54,981
Oh, you want me
  to calm down.

1432
01:01:55,048 --> 01:01:56,583
Calm down, Mr. Calvert.

1433
01:01:56,649 --> 01:01:58,218
Calm down.
      I can calm down.

1434
01:01:58,284 --> 01:01:59,219
That calm enough
       for you?

1435
01:01:59,285 --> 01:02:01,654
What about that?

1436
01:02:01,721 --> 01:02:03,957
[struggling
and yelling]

1437
01:02:04,024 --> 01:02:05,258
Get him on the other side.

1438
01:02:05,325 --> 01:02:06,292
What are you doing?

1439
01:02:06,359 --> 01:02:08,028
I got a broken hand.

1440
01:02:08,094 --> 01:02:09,162
Put me--

1441
01:02:09,229 --> 01:02:10,764
I didn't
 do anything wrong.

1442
01:02:10,830 --> 01:02:12,399
÷ ÷Orderly!
  Let me go.

1443
01:02:12,465 --> 01:02:13,767
Come on.
Come on.

