You know, Artie,
I got to tell you,

1445
01:02:18,071 --> 01:02:19,739
I feel really bad
about what happened

1446
01:02:19,806 --> 01:02:22,042
at the apartment today,
and I want you to know that,

1447
01:02:22,108 --> 01:02:24,310
you know,
I wasn't mad at you.

1448
01:02:24,377 --> 01:02:26,846
See, I was...
I was mad...

1449
01:02:29,349 --> 01:02:30,483
[sighing]
Man, Artie,

1450
01:02:30,550 --> 01:02:33,319
I really screwed things up
between Nina and me.

1451
01:02:33,386 --> 01:02:35,021
You have no idea.

1452
01:02:37,891 --> 01:02:41,061
Actually, you probably do,
don't you?

1453
01:02:52,105 --> 01:02:53,907
Hey, Artie.

1454
01:02:53,973 --> 01:02:56,743
I got to know.

1455
01:02:56,810 --> 01:02:59,012
That stuff
you were saying today,

1456
01:02:59,079 --> 01:03:04,250
about you and me,
      you know,

1457
01:03:04,317 --> 01:03:07,020
about your wife,
    that was just crazy, right?

1458
01:03:07,087 --> 01:03:10,090
Just some
  big misunderstanding, right?

1459
01:03:10,156 --> 01:03:11,257
[footsteps]

1460
01:03:14,260 --> 01:03:15,195
Who are you?

1461
01:03:15,261 --> 01:03:16,896
I'm a friend.

1462
01:03:18,998 --> 01:03:21,001
I've never
met you before.

1463
01:03:21,067 --> 01:03:22,569
Paul Venezelos.

1464
01:03:22,635 --> 01:03:24,337
Hi.

1465
01:03:24,404 --> 01:03:26,206
Michael Reilly.

1466
01:03:26,272 --> 01:03:28,041
I'm the guy
that took him here.

1467
01:03:28,108 --> 01:03:29,342
I'm a cop.

1468
01:03:29,409 --> 01:03:30,377
Oh, thank you.

1469
01:03:30,443 --> 01:03:31,478
Yeah.

1470
01:03:31,544 --> 01:03:33,480
So how's he doing?

1471
01:03:33,546 --> 01:03:35,115
He's stable.

1472
01:03:38,718 --> 01:03:40,086
All right.

1473
01:03:40,153 --> 01:03:41,988
Well, thanks for sitting
      with him.

1474
01:03:42,055 --> 01:03:43,323
It was good to meet you.

1475
01:03:43,390 --> 01:03:45,525
Yeah, of course.

1476
01:03:51,998 --> 01:03:52,999
Mike.

1477
01:03:54,034 --> 01:03:55,735
Yeah?

1478
01:03:55,802 --> 01:03:57,337
He didn't give you
  some cockamamy story

1479
01:03:57,404 --> 01:03:59,639
about you being
my reincarnated mother, did he?

1480
01:04:02,809 --> 01:04:04,978
He did, didn't he?

1481
01:04:06,613 --> 01:04:08,982
He's been doing that
to some poor unsuspecting chump

1482
01:04:09,049 --> 01:04:10,583
every Christmas
 since she died.

1483
01:04:12,452 --> 01:04:13,553
Well, look,

1484
01:04:13,620 --> 01:04:14,854
I promise I'll let him know

1485
01:04:14,921 --> 01:04:16,589
that you were here
  when he wakes up, all right?

1486
01:04:16,656 --> 01:04:18,825
Yeah.

1487
01:04:18,892 --> 01:04:20,694
I appreciate it.

1488
01:04:29,436 --> 01:04:37,377
[melancholy music]
    ^^ ^^

