      Can't believe
    you're still here.

1490
01:05:33,667 --> 01:05:34,801
So he likes to tell people

1491
01:05:34,868 --> 01:05:36,469
they're your
reincarnated mother, huh?

1492
01:05:36,536 --> 01:05:37,771
Yeah.

1493
01:05:37,837 --> 01:05:39,739
Always around Christmas.

1494
01:05:44,344 --> 01:05:45,578
Look, I'm sorry
about your mother

1495
01:05:45,645 --> 01:05:46,846
and all that happened.

1496
01:05:48,915 --> 01:05:50,617
He told you what happened?

1497
01:05:50,684 --> 01:05:52,485
Yeah, a little.

1498
01:05:52,552 --> 01:05:54,154
You know,
he mentioned it once.

1499
01:05:54,220 --> 01:05:55,255
Wow.

