 Morning.

1531
01:08:57,804 --> 01:08:59,172
Morning.

1532
01:08:59,239 --> 01:09:01,341
How you feeling?

1533
01:09:01,408 --> 01:09:02,942
Rose.

1534
01:09:03,009 --> 01:09:04,544
Charlie,
if you have to leave,

1535
01:09:04,611 --> 01:09:05,779
I understand,
really.

1536
01:09:05,845 --> 01:09:07,147
It's fine.

1537
01:09:07,213 --> 01:09:09,049
Look, I made it
through the night, didn't I?

1538
01:09:09,115 --> 01:09:10,917
Yes, you have.

1539
01:09:10,984 --> 01:09:13,253
But is that
  what you really wanted?

1540
01:09:13,319 --> 01:09:14,521
Just to make it
      through the night

1541
01:09:14,587 --> 01:09:16,556
and that's all?

1542
01:09:16,623 --> 01:09:20,326
Well, I suppose
I'd like to think

1543
01:09:20,393 --> 01:09:22,328
that my life matters.

1544
01:09:22,395 --> 01:09:24,531
Oh, your life matters.

1545
01:09:24,597 --> 01:09:26,099
You've touched
other people's lives

1546
01:09:26,166 --> 01:09:27,600
in ways you don't
      even realize.

1547
01:09:27,667 --> 01:09:29,102
[scoffing]
How do you know that?

1548
01:09:29,169 --> 01:09:30,236
Because you touched
my life.

1549
01:09:30,303 --> 01:09:32,405
You're just
being nice, Charlie.

1550
01:09:32,472 --> 01:09:33,606
No, Rose,
      I'm not.

1551
01:09:33,673 --> 01:09:34,641
It's more than that.

1552
01:09:34,708 --> 01:09:36,843
You saved me, Rose.

1553
01:09:38,645 --> 01:09:39,746
