where God was,

1554
01:09:39,813 --> 01:09:42,015
and the next thing you know,
  there you are

1555
01:09:42,082 --> 01:09:44,250
at the bedside
   of a complete stranger

1556
01:09:44,317 --> 01:09:47,520
telling him you love him
    with such meaning.

1557
01:09:47,587 --> 01:09:49,322
And then I knew
      God was there

1558
01:09:49,389 --> 01:09:51,825
in that room
      with you.

1559
01:09:51,891 --> 01:09:53,226
You were there?

1560
01:09:53,293 --> 01:09:54,361
?
  Yeah.

1561
01:09:54,427 --> 01:09:56,196
Why did you do that,
  Rose?

1562
01:09:58,198 --> 01:09:59,933
I...

1563
01:10:03,069 --> 01:10:04,771
Because he was just so alone,

1564
01:10:04,838 --> 01:10:07,207
and...

1565
01:10:09,209 --> 01:10:12,078
I guess I know
    what it feels like.

1566
